question: Will CZ be arrested by April 30?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if co-founder of Binance Changpeng Zhao (CZ) is arrested by April 30, 2023 (ET). Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

The primary resolution source for this market will be a consensus of credible reporting, however official information from the governments involved in any action against CZ and information from CZ's and Binance's legal representatives will also be used.

question: Will Binance.US shut down by April 30?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if Binance.US announces it will remove the ability to open new spot positions for a majority of its listed assets by April 30, 2023 (ET). Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If Binance.US announces by April 30, 2023 that they will remove the ability to open new spot positions for a majority of its listed assets, the market will resolve to “Yes” regardless of whether the removal occurs after that date.

Whether or not Binance.US continues to accept new accounts will have no bearing on this market's resolution. Outages due to maintenance or bugs will not suffice to resolve this market to “Yes” - it must be a deliberate announcement including removal of the ability to open new spot positions.

The primary resolution source will be information from Binance.US, Binance.US's legal representatives, Changpeng Zhao (CZ), and/or Brian Shroder, however a consensus of credible reporting will also be used.

question: Will $ETH moon after Shanghai?
description:
Update: The 1 minute candle encapsulating the Shanghai Upgrade had a close price of 1917.23. 

This market will resolve to "Yes" if 1 week after the Shanghai Upgrade, the price of $ETH is at least 3% more than it was at the time of the upgrade. Otherwise the market will resolve to "No."

"1 week after the Shanghai Upgrade" is defined by exactly 7 days (168 hours) after the Shanghai Upgrade. The Shanghai upgrade refers to the the hard fork implementing EIP-4895. If the Shanghai Upgrade does not occur by December 31, 2023, the market will resolve to 50-50.

The resolution source for this market is https://www.binance.com/en/trade/ETH_USDT, namely the 1 minute candle close prices which encapsulate the Shanghai Upgrade time and 1 week after.
